  "prompt": "I lost my Jio barcode how can I regenerate?",
  "response": "To regenerate your Jio barcode, you can follow these steps:\n\n1. Through MyJio App:\n- Open the MyJio app\n- Go to the 'Get Jio SIM' section\n- Select 'Regenerate Barcode'\n- Follow the on-screen instructions\n\n2. Online through Jio Website:\n- Visit the official Jio website\n- Go to the SIM activation section\n- Select 'Regenerate Barcode'\n- Enter your mobile number\n\n3. At Jio Store/Retail Outlet:\n- Visit nearest Jio Store or authorized retailer\n- Request barcode regeneration\n- Carry your ID proof for verification\n\n4. Through Customer Care:\n- Call Jio Customer Care at 198\n- Request barcode regeneration\n- Follow their instructions\n\n5. SMS Method:\n- Send SMS 'BARCODE' to 198\n- You'll receive regeneration details\n\nImportant: You'll need to provide your registered mobile number and valid ID proof for verification during the process.\n\nNote: The exact steps might vary slightly, so it's best to check the most recent process through official Jio channels.",
